## Import


An existing resource can be imported using its type token, name, and identifier, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import azure-native:securityinsights:DataConnector 73e01a99-5cd7-4139-a149-9f2736ff2ab5 /subscriptions/d0cfe6b2-9ac0-4464-9919-dccaee2e48c0/resourceGroups/myRg/providers/Microsoft.OperationalIinsights/workspaces/myWorkspace/providers/Microsoft.SecurityInsights/dataConnectors/73e01a99-5cd7-4139-a149-9f2736ff2ab5 
```
